{"tid":95901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友話佢食咗個鬼妹 重要房錢佢比","createTime":"2017-01-26T11:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T15:13:27.000Z","uid":65593,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96f57a6e24e330a89838da816fa2bd06327fb7b4","tid":95901,"uid":65593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"小弟個朋友係啲運動戇尻 四肢發達頭腦膠膠地嗰啲<br />\n早兩日同埋朋友b同佢食飯 運動戇尻興高采烈咁同我地講食咗個「鬼妹 」 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 運動戇尻 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友b<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂 呢排我係交友app識咗個鬼妹 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嘩咁撚正 估你唔撚到喎 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係啊 想試下啲異國風情嘛 前晚去爆房 嘩成晚都冇停過手啊 又大波 又淫 腳都軟blablablabla<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你就好啦幾舊水房錢有洋妞食 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咩啊 房錢佢比埋啊 我拍拍蘿友走咗啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嘩咁撚淫賤？你唔好講咁撚多啦 拎啲圖黎睇下先啦含家產<br />\n就係呢個時候 惡夢就黎喇 佢打開電話相簿 我眼尾見到啲啡啡黑黑既人 仆街原來賓妹黎 <br />\n係呢一秒 我同朋友b都呆咁feel到胃酸倒流既感覺 係 係好撚想當場嘔出黎<br />\n運動戇尻不停問：點呀點呀 係咪好撚正啊<br />\n由於我同朋友b都唔令到運動戇尻懢介 <br />\n所以拿拿聲同朋友b食完個飯就走咗<br />\n宜家好怕佢四圍同人講我同朋友b都話個賓妹正 點算"},{"pid":"fcc7eb2420a70e909da8e0ccb722ff2b1d4f7c44","tid":95901,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"鬼妹同賓妹都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d18b1626db53e12a99ca17e2391e6ff9b198af","tid":95901,"uid":65593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼妹同賓妹都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個人本身係膠膠地 係估唔到佢膠得咁澈底"},{"pid":"10869f7bd5db9866a9e15a6e94daeac7a8624890","tid":95901,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"過多排可能有個小黑人叫佢做老豆"},{"pid":"f14e9babdab1599e39016fbcc48cc63d90de6b2c","tid":95901,"uid":65593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多排可能有個小黑人叫佢做老豆</blockquote><br />\n可能佢會好自豪咁話自己生咗個鬼仔"},{"pid":"8d502520440d50e0025177a8281e4d3e28d34b96","tid":95901,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"啲icon 真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b003b04994a1f859af7bb2edd4d21a4d6abda97b","tid":95901,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲icon 真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d962b5af637d1919e21c1706b0320c09998e86","tid":95901,"uid":76650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲icon 真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爸爸"},{"pid":"e601a74d8c9b51cd33b98b286a4ef93baafa1769","tid":95901,"uid":65593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲icon 真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爸爸</blockquote><br />\n我當時個樣真係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ea7772277db0d94c0cc646957e5d3eb290a980","tid":95901,"uid":53568,"like":0,"disli